room_title: Escape room "Mr. Dupree’s Office" by Escape STL in St. Louis
room_address: 2650 S Hanley Road St. Louis, MO 63144
room_description: You are on an elite team of fellow CIA agents assigned with the task of gathering incriminating evidence from the office of international business man, Mr. Dupree. Our Intelligence team could only get you into Mr. Dupree’s office for 60 minutes. You must get out before Mr. Dupree returns or the case is blown!
